data.title: Cool celebrity baby girl names
data.meta_description: Check out our list of the top cool celebrity girl baby names. From unique names like Anniston to traditional names and trendy names, check out which celebrity baby girl name made our list.
data.text:
From Anniston to Adele, you will love the cool celebrity baby girl names that made our list. Sugar and spice and everything nice, that’s what little girls are made ofâ€¦ and in 2009 there were plenty of little ladies born to celebrities. Here’s a round-up of the baby girls who made their debut this past year.

From traditional girl names to unique girl names, we saw a variety of baby girl names in 2009. Check out our alphabetical list of the top cool celebrity girl names. Wondering what cool celebrity boy names made our list? Find out here!
